{"tid":885762,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇邊款耳機比較耐用冇咁易爛？","createTime":"2018-11-01T14:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T14:29:08.000Z","uid":67462,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ae8372325ee9f9e82c640d12ecb1f060e452ac","tid":885762,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"近幾年用親d耳機都唔係用到聽唔倒歌而換，係用到爛<br />\n以前用過beats既入耳式同埋頭戴式既，前者爛線，後者個耳罩爛<br />\n跟住就買左個ATH既headphone就好似下面幾幅圖咁甩曬皮（想問下個頭濕果陣帶headphone會唔會有影響？）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeohSvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeohSvw.jpg&h=c37a2751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zaa8eLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaa8eLa.jpg&h=4190b339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KLcZmqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKLcZmqb.jpg&h=e8da945c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後買左個SE425就係個外殼中間d膠甩左，所以尋晚用完耳機係隻耳度除番出黎果陣就斷開一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2MGzLO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2MGzLO.jpg&h=68df13a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小弟預2000蚊左右，入耳式，音質呢，正常唔好太差啦，最緊要耐用，用倒兩年或以上就最好，有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心很累，d耳機又貴又唔耐用，垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52267cd1995cd8103177d410f14b8cc9b26b3f0b","tid":885762,"uid":65400,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T21:15:49.000Z","msg":"ie800"},{"pid":"05fd80a8fd9749b762edf6fcc0bed72348f1fc21","tid":885762,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":